BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:pwBPhvgHdRZgklQEvMeLM
SUMMARY:First Thursday - April
DTSTAMP:20260314T140403Z
DTSTART:20260402T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Visit MOHAI on the First Thursday of every month for free admis
	sion to the museum’s permanent exhibits between 5—8 pm. \\nFree admission 
	includes access to all of MOHAI’s award winning exhibits\\\, including our
	 temporary displays Riding Together: 135 Years of Cycling in Seattle\\\, T
	ADAIMA: I’m Home and special exhibit Kickstands Up! 125 Years of Motorcycl
	ing in the PNW. Advance online tickets are not required\\\, but may be res
	erved below. \\nFree admission also includes access to two special present
	ations of Living Voices in the Joshua Green Theater at 5:30 and 6:30pm. Se
	ats are first-come first-served.\n\nhttps://mohai.org/event/first-thursday
	-april/\n\nFrom MOHAI - Museum of History & Industry
URL:https://mohai.org/event/first-thursday-april/
LOCATION:MOHAI\\\, MOHAI - 860 Terry Ave N\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98109\\\,
